  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink301">
<l>mālveḷ ḷōttirattu maiyil vāliṇa</l>
<l>raruñcurañ celvōr ceṉṉik kūṭṭu</l>
<l>mavvarai yiṟakkuvai yāyiṉ</l>
<l>maivarai nāṭa varuntuvaḷ peritē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from the country of the dark mountains!</l> 
<l>If you pass over those mountains, where travelers across the difficult desert </l>
<l>cover their heads with flawless white flower clusters of the Lodh tree, </l>
<l>[that has] dark [foliage] and light [blossoms] – she will suffer a lot.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
